-a[mode to use while on AC power]
-b[mode to use while on battery power]
-i[CPU idle percent level when begin to degrade performance]
-n[mode to use normally when the AC line state is unknown]
-p[polling interval (in milliseconds) for AC line state and system idle levels]
-P[alternative pidfile]
-r[CPU idle percent level where to increase performance]
-v[verbose mode]
